channel.title: How come i can't edit frankenstein's castle?
channel.description:
Hello, I wanted to use frankenstein's castle for part of my server but i can't edit it at all... I can't make door cases, delete the doors, etc...
I'm using Ayudascape V.3 if that doesn't support Frankenstein's castle please tell me :)
Thank you, -Zaron
